				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"><span style="font-weight: bold">Question</span>: Textual Confirmation has been working well, up until recently. I am now getting a large amount of registrations and spam messages posted.
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Answer</span>: Try to change the questions because some classes of them seem been compromised:
<br />

<br />
* With yes/no/true/false answers
<br />
* Probably arithmetics (1+2, etc)
<br />
* Probably with colors name answers
<br />

<br />
Also, I released <a href="http://bbantispam.com/atc/" target="_blank" class="postlink">Advanced Textual Confirmation</a>. This tool implements more checks and can protect from the recent generation of spam bots.<br />_________________<br />Oleg Parashchenko, bbAntiSpam
